  "prompt": "Which is the best institute in India for doing a hands on course in ethical hacking?",
  "response": "There are several reputable institutes in India that offer hands-on courses in ethical hacking. While \"best\" can vary based on personal preferences, location, and specific course offerings, here are some of the well-regarded institutions you might consider:\n\n1. **Indian School of Ethical Hacking (ISOEH)** - Offers specialized courses in ethical hacking and cybersecurity with practical exposure.\n\n2. **Institute of Information Security (IIS)** - Provides a range of courses in ethical hacking and cybersecurity, focusing on practical skills.\n\n3. **Cybersecurity and Data Science Institute (CDSI)** - Known for offering hands-on training in cybersecurity, including ethical hacking.\n\n4. **Edureka** - An online platform that offers comprehensive ethical hacking courses with hands-on experience and project work.\n\n5. **Simplilearn** - Offers online courses in ethical hacking, which include hands-on labs and practical projects.\n\n6. **NIIT** - Provides cybersecurity courses that include ethical hacking with practical training.\n\n7. **Certified Ethical Hacker (CEH) by EC-Council** - While not an institute, this certification is highly recognized and many training centers in India offer CEH courses that include extensive hands-on training.\n\nBefore enrolling, consider checking the course curriculum, faculty qualifications, reviews from former students, and the availability of lab facilities. It\u2019s also beneficial to seek institutes that provide placement assistance or industry connections.",
